snippet.title: sploder: i hate nebraska
snippet.description:
archiving all the games i made on sploder.com before the website gets deleted at the end of 2020!

http://www.sploder.com/games/members/meowmeowfurrycat/play/i-hate-nebraska/

made this one when i was 12. i was putting out a bunch of games whose sole purpose was to exploit counterintuitive glitches & whose sole audience was deeply enfranchised players. i do not actually hate nebraska and i can't explain where the title came from haha
